                </mxCell>
                <mxCell id="yuK76GC2vzyNwLmF7uwJ-23" style="rounded=0;orthogonalLoop=1;jettySize=auto;html=1;endArrow=none;endFill=0;exitX=0.5;exitY=1;exitDx=0;exitDy=0;entryX=0.5;entryY=0;entryDx=0;entryDy=0;verticalAlign=top;" parent="1" source="yuK76GC2vzyNwLmF7uwJ-1" target="yuK76GC2vzyNwLmF7uwJ-22" edge="1">
                    <mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry">
                        <mxPoint x="1417" y="1732" as="sourcePoint"/>
                        <mxPoint x="1537" y="1802" as="targetPoint"/>
                    </mxGeometry>
                </mxCell>
                <mxCell id="yuK76GC2vzyNwLmF7uwJ-27" value="&lt;div style=&quot;line-height: 200%;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Current process:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;What are the typical process steps of users to accomplish offline data analysis?&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;How do users typically start their notebook with? Totally blank? Template from DA/instruments? Cookbook recipe?&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;color: rgb(244, 244, 244);&quot;&gt;What artifacts do users typically produce during offline analysis? Are they also preparing documentation for the data and their analysis artifacts&lt;br&gt;(similar to a README file on GitHub/GitLab)?&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;color: rgb(244, 244, 244);&quot;&gt;How long do users typically analyze this data offline? I read between days and months.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=top;rounded=0;" parent="1" vertex="1">
                    <mxGeometry x="1058.5" y="2044" width="913" height="177" as="geometry"/>
                </mxCell>
                <mxCell id="yuK76GC2vzyNwLmF7uwJ-31" value="&lt;div style=&quot;line-height: 200%;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Current challenges:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;What are knowledge-related challenges during offline data analysis (e.g., documentation, communication and support, clarity of tool features, requirements of users):&lt;/li&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;For users?&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;For DA members?&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;For other EuXFEL members, e.g., instruments groups?&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;What are the biggest challenges at the moment?&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=top;rounded=0;" parent="1" vertex="1">
                    <mxGeometry x="1025.5" y="4176" width="932" height="189" as="geometry"/>
                </mxCell>
                <mxCell id="yuK76GC2vzyNwLmF7uwJ-37" value="&lt;div style=&quot;line-height: 200%;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Research Questions&lt;/b&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;RQ1: What &lt;b&gt;knowledge-related challenges&lt;/b&gt; do EuXFEL users encounter during &lt;b&gt;offline&lt;/b&gt; data analysis?&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;RQ2: What are the&amp;nbsp;&lt;b&gt;requirements of an AI agent&lt;/b&gt;&amp;nbsp;that addresses the challenges?&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;RQ3: What&amp;nbsp;&lt;b&gt;design recommendations&lt;/b&gt;&amp;nbsp;can be derived from deploying and evaluating the&amp;nbsp;&lt;b&gt;AI agent in practice&lt;/b&gt;?&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=top;rounded=0;" parent="1" vertex="1">
                    <mxGeometry x="1020" y="525" width="711" height="139" as="geometry"/>
                </mxCell>
                <mxCell id="yuK76GC2vzyNwLmF7uwJ-41" value="&lt;div style=&quot;line-height: 200%;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Methodology&lt;/b&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;Design Science Research &lt;/b&gt;with six (repeatable) activities:&lt;/li&gt;&lt;ol&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(237, 237, 237));&quot;&gt;Problem identification and motivation (RQ1)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(237, 237, 237));&quot;&gt;Definition of the objectives for a solution&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;(RQ2)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(237, 237, 237));&quot;&gt;Design and development&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;(RQ3)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(237, 237, 237));&quot;&gt;Demonstration&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;(RQ3)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(237, 237, 237));&quot;&gt;Evaluation&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;(RQ3)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(237, 237, 237));&quot;&gt;Communication (paper publication)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ol&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;Today: focus on problem identification (RQ1)&lt;br&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;RQ1: What&amp;nbsp;&lt;b&gt;knowledge-related challenges&lt;/b&gt;&amp;nbsp;do EuXFEL users encounter during&amp;nbsp;&lt;b&gt;offline data analysis&lt;/b&gt;?&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Method: focus group&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Created artifacts: mind maps&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;Information on data protection:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;No personal information from individuals required&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Demographic information that will be reported:&lt;/li&gt;&lt;ol&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(237, 237, 237));&quot;&gt;&quot;Focus group session was conducted with the Data Analysis group at EuXFEL.&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(237, 237, 237));&quot;&gt;&quot;[X] group members participated in the session.&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ol&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=top;rounded=0;" parent="1" vertex="1">
                    <mxGeometry x="1020" y="1022" width="781" height="443" as="geometry"/>
                </mxCell>
                <mxCell id="yuK76GC2vzyNwLmF7uwJ-47" value="&lt;div style=&quot;line-height: 200%;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Context&lt;/b&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Tim Fuchs (formerly Tim Puhlfürß)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;PhD project in Informatics at Uni Hamburg, collaboration with EuXFEL and DASHH Graduate School&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Focus on knowledge exchange between software engineers and users (especially with&amp;nbsp;&lt;b&gt;documentation&lt;/b&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Previous studies at EuXFEL:&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Problem-focused:&amp;nbsp;&lt;b&gt;Questionnaire&lt;/b&gt;&amp;nbsp;about challenges in knowledge exchange&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Solution-focused:&amp;nbsp;&lt;b&gt;AI-powered VS Code extension&lt;/b&gt;&amp;nbsp;to generate documentation comments in source code&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Solution-focused:&amp;nbsp;&lt;b&gt;AI-powered knowledge base&lt;/b&gt;&amp;nbsp;to accelerate information retrieval from issue trackers and documents&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Final study of PhD project:&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Solution-focused:&amp;nbsp;&lt;b&gt;AI-powered tool to support users during offline data analysis&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=top;rounded=0;" parent="1" vertex="1">
                    <mxGeometry x="1020" y="110" width="735" height="281" as="geometry"/>
                </mxCell>
