                <mxCell id="UNV8H-uVcZEB_V4CqLyU-3" value="&lt;div style=&quot;line-height: 200%;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Survey/Interviews during EuXFEL&#39;s Users&#39; Meeting (2026-01-27&lt;/b&gt;&lt;b style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;):&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;line-height: 200%;&quot;&gt;&lt;ol&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;Have you previously used EuXFEL’s data analysis tools&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;(e.g., Python library EXtra, myMDC, DAMNIT)?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;What positive aspects of the offline data analysis process have you experienced? Please focus on aspects related to the exchange of knowledge/information (e.g., support from EuXFEL members, the information provided by the tools, and the tool documentation).&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;What negative aspects of the offline data analysis process have you experienced? Please focus on aspects related to the exchange of knowledge/information.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Imagine you could use a specialized AI tool, which is similar to ChatGPT but provided by EuXFEL. What tasks should the tool support you with during offline data analysis?&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Are you a user or a member of EuXFEL?&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;How many experiments have you participated in at EuXFEL?&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ol&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;b&gt;Responses:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;2 users&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;5 members (instrument scientists)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;All had experience with EXtra.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;b&gt;Debriefing:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Reflect on challenges and requirements mentioned by users&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Add further challenges and requirements&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Prioritize requirements&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=top;rounded=0;" parent="1" vertex="1">
